'''明應地震'''（{{jpn|j=明応地震|kn=めいおうじしん|rm=Meiō Jishin}}）是指1498年9月20日<ref name="IISEE">{{cite web|url=http://iisee.kenken.go.jp/utsu/utsuweq_bak_eng.html|title=IISEE search page|last=IISEE|accessdate=2011年1月6日|archive-date=2010年7月21日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100721030928/http://iisee.kenken.go.jp/utsu/utsuweq_bak_eng.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="NGDC"/>（[[明應_(日本)|明應]]7年8月25日）日本於當地時間在上午8點，在[[伊豆半島|伊豆半島]]外海發生了強烈[[地震|地震]]。地震規模估計是8.6[[表面波規模|M<sub>S</sub>]]，並且也引發了巨大[[海嘯|海嘯]]襲擊陸地。在明應地震造成的罹難人數並不確定，根據當時有紀錄到，罹難人數有26,000人到31,000人之間<ref name="NGDC_t">{{cite web|url=http://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/results?eq_0=7383&t=101650&s=18&d=99,91,95,93&nd=display|title=Comments for the Tsunami Event|last=NGDC|accessdate=2011年1月6日|archive-date=2017年8月3日|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170803211651/https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/nndc/struts/results?eq_0=7383&t=101650&s=18&d=99,91,95,93&nd=display|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==地震背景==
[[File:RuptureAreasNankaiMegathrust.png|thumb]]

引發了明應地震的[[南海海槽|南海海槽]]與[[本州|本州]]南部海岸線平行，這也顯示了[[歐亞板塊|歐亞板塊]]與[[菲律賓海板塊|菲律賓海板塊]]發生了推擠。這2個板塊互相推擠邊界會導致了發生許多地震，但其中1些屬於為[[大型逆衝區地震|大型逆衝區地震]]。在南海海槽有5個不同的地區（A、B、C、D、E）就很有可能會發生破裂<ref name="Ando">{{cite journal|last=Ando|first=M.|year=1975|title=Source mechanisms and tectonic significance of historical earthquakes along the nankai trough, Japan|journal=Tectonophysics|volume=27|issue=2|pages=119–140|url=http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6V72-488946W-V&_user=7763359&_coverDate=06%2F30%2F1975&_rdoc=2&_fmt=high&_orig=browse&_srch=doc-info(%23toc%235830%231975%23999729997%23411366%23FLP%23display%23Volume)&_cdi=5830&_sort=d&_docanchor=&_ct=7&_acct=C000054050&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=7763359&md5=de6402adea71f15ca0590abd8072d91b|accessdate=2009-11-13|doi=10.1016/0040-1951(75)90102-X|bibcode=1975Tectp..27..119A|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190111144333/http://www.sciencedirect.com/science?_ob=ArticleURL&_udi=B6V72-488946W-V&_user=7763359&_coverDate=06%2F30%2F1975&_rdoc=2&_fmt=high&_orig=browse&_srch=doc-info(%23toc%235830%231975%23999729997%23411366%23FLP%23display%23Volume)&_cdi=5830&_sort=d&_docanchor=&_ct=7&_acct=C000054050&_version=1&_urlVersion=0&_userid=7763359&md5=de6402adea71f15ca0590abd8072d91b|archive-date=2019-01-11|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="Ishibashi">{{cite journal|last=Ishibashi|first=K.|year=2004|title=Status of historical seismology in Japan|journal=Annals of Geophysics|volume=47|issue=2/3|pages=339–368|url=http://www.earth-prints.org/bitstream/2122/763/1/02Ishibashi.pdf|accessdate=2009-11-22|archive-date=2019-10-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191025033415/https://www.earth-prints.org/bitstream/2122/763/1/02Ishibashi.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>，這些地區在過去1,300年之中曾單獨或者是1起破裂<ref name="Sieh">{{cite book|last=Sieh|first=K.E.|title=A Review of Geological Evidence for Recurrence Times of Large Earthquakes|year=1981|url=http://www.gps.caltech.edu/~sieh/pubs_docs/papers/P81b.pdf|accessdate=2009-11-13|archive-date=2010-06-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100604120819/http://www.gps.caltech.edu/~sieh/pubs_docs/papers/P81b.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。除了在[[1854年南海大地震|1854年南海大地震]]之後，另外在1944年（[[1944年東南海地震|1944年東南海地震]]）和1946年（[[1946年南海道大地震|1946年南海道大地震]]）也有類似的地震發生，這些地震都是先從南海海槽東北段就開始了破裂，之後就延伸到了南海海槽西南段<ref name="Kaneda">{{cite journal|last=Kaneda|first=Y.|author2=Kawaguchi, K.   Araki, E.   Matsumoto, H.   Nakamura, T.   Kamiya, S.   Hori, T.  &  Baba, T.|year=2007|title=Precise real-time observatory and simulating phenomena of earthquakes and tsunamis around the Nankai Trough - Towards the understanding of mega thrust earthquakes|journal=Underwater Technology and Workshop on Scientific Use of Submarine Cables and Related Technologies, 2007. Symposium on|pages=299–300|url=http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/freeabs_all.jsp?arnumber=4231136|accessdate=2009-11-13|archive-date=2012-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120315231203/http://ieeexplore.ieee.org/xpl/freeabs_all.jsp?arnumber=4231136|dead-url=no}}</ref>。這位科學家他認為：該次明應地震是南海海槽C、D和E地區破裂所導致了發生的。

==海嘯==
該次地震也引發了地面劇烈搖動，從[[房總半島|房總半島]]到[[紀伊半島|紀伊半島]]也有地震的紀錄。還引發的巨大海嘯襲擊了[[駿河灣|駿河灣]]和[[鎌倉|鎌倉]]地區，在江梨、小川都遭受到了浪高高度為8公尺的巨大海嘯侵襲，在[[伊勢|伊勢]]、[[志摩|志摩]]等地巨大[[海嘯|海嘯]]高度為6公尺到10公尺，在[[志摩半島|志摩半島]][[鳥羽市|鳥羽市]]國崎町巨大海嘯高度則達到了為15公尺<ref>[http://opi-rina.chunichi.co.jp/topic/20110407-4.html 中日新聞2011/4/7] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130517012214/http://opi-rina.chunichi.co.jp/topic/20110407-4.html |date=2013-05-17 }} [[中日新聞|中日新聞]] {{lang|ja|500年前の明応地震 識者「想定見直しを」}}</ref>。明應地震摧毀了[[高德院|高德院]][[佛|佛]]像<ref name="Ishabashi_2">{{cite book|last=Ishabashi|first=K.|editor=Simpson D.W. & Pichards P.G.|title=Earthquake prediction: an international review|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=z7RF-9gKyJEC&pg=PA324&dq=1498+nankai+earthquake&hl=en&ei=HALMTLzyBIXsOf366dsB&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=1498%20nankai%20earthquake&f=false|series=Maurice Ewing Series|volume=4|year=1981|publisher=American Geophysical Union|isbn=978-0-87590-403-0|pages=323-324|chapter=Specification of a soon-to-occur seismic faulting in the Tokai District, central Japan, based on seismotectoncs|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113040244/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=z7RF-9gKyJEC&pg=PA324&dq=1498+nankai+earthquake&hl=en&ei=HALMTLzyBIXsOf366dsB&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=1498%20nankai%20earthquake&f=false|archivedate=2012-11-13}}</ref>，在南海地區也有嚴重的地面液化紀錄<ref name="Rikitake">{{cite journal|last=Rikitake|first=T|year=1999|title=Probability of a great earthquake to recur in the Tokai district, Japan:|journal=Earth Planets Space|volume=51|pages=147–157|url=http://www.terrapub.co.jp/journals/EPS/pdf/5103/51030147.pdf|accessdate=30 October 2010|bibcode=1999EP&S...51..147R|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303225750/http://www.terrapub.co.jp/journals/EPS/pdf/5103/51030147.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在相模海槽與[[伊豆半島|伊豆半島]]的沿海平原也都發現了巨大海嘯沉積物<ref name="Komatsubara">{{cite book|last1=Komatsubara|first1=J.|last2=Fujiwara|first2=O.|editor=Satake K., Okal E.A. & Borrero J.C.|title=Tsunami and Its Hazards in the Indian and Pacific Oceans|url=http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=HME_XQS-D-cC&pg=PA494&dq=1498+meio+nankai+earthquake&hl=en&ei=PDjMTNvOFc_sObO5qM0B&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&sqi=2&ved=0CD4Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=1498%20meio%20nankai%20earthquake&f=false|series=Pageophys topical volumes|volume=164|year=2007|isbn=978-3-7643-8363-3|page=494|chapter=Overview of Holocene tsunami deposits along the Nankai, Sugura and Sagami Troughs, southwest Japan|access-date=2015-05-06|archive-date=2012-11-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121113040812/http://books.google.co.uk/books?id=HME_XQS-D-cC&pg=PA494&dq=1498+meio+nankai+earthquake&hl=en&ei=PDjMTNvOFc_sObO5qM0B&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&sqi=2&ved=0CD4Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=1498%20meio%20nankai%20earthquake&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。鳥羽市當地居民在地震之後到移居高地，也遠離海岸線。

